    Serializable, Comparable<HtmlTag>

    public enum HtmlTag
extends Enum<HtmlTag>
    Enum representing HTML tags. The intent of this class is to embody the semantics of W3C HTML 4.01 to the extent supported/used by javadoc. In time, we may wish to transition javadoc and doclint to using HTML 5. This is derivative of com.sun.tools.doclets.formats.html.markup.HtmlTag. Eventually, these two should be merged back together, and possibly made public.
    另请参阅:
    HTML 4.01 Specification, HTML 5 Specification, WAI-ARIA Specification, WAI-ARIA Recommendations Table
